          <p></p>
            <p>Prof. (Dr.) Devesh Kishore has more than 45 years of experience of training, research & production in the field of Mass Communication & Journalism. He possess Ph.D with specialisation in Development Broadcasting & Master in Development Communication.</p>
            <p>He has worked as a teacher, researcher and broadcaster. Worked with the Indian Institute of Mass Communication (IIMC). Prof. Kishore has even worked as Communications Head with NAARM. His years of experience and expertise include working as Director & Prof. Communications at Indira Gandhi National Open Univ. (IGNOU) followed by working as a Dean at IMS, NOIDA. He became Prof. Emeritus at M C National Univ. of Journalism & Communication, Bhopal in 2010.</p>
            <p>Prof. Kishore has presented papers in  several  International conferences, workshops & seminars at  London, Tokyo, Singapore, Thailand, Washington, Chicago & Phoenix.</p>
            <p>He has guided several International , National Research Projects & researches leading to Ph.D  Till now 12 students have been awarded Ph.D under his guidance by MC National University of Journalism & Mass Communication, Bhopal; Gorakhpur University & Shimla University .He helped the UGC Panel in selecting research proposals & developed Bachelors & Masters Programme in Communication which was readily accepted by several universities.</p>
